Key Match Events: Two wickets in a single Arshdeep Singh over!
Ashwin picks two in an over!
Miscellaneous Highlights: India go top of the Group 1 with big win
Others: Arshdeep Singh didn't get his hattrick and ended up conceding 14 runs off the last over
The win takes India to top of Group 2
Netherlands only went as far as 123 for 9 in their 20 overs as R Ashwin, Axar, Arshdeep and Bhuvneshwar picked two wicket each while Shami got one

Rohit Sharma is gone. His PowerPlay woes continue. Since October 2020, he's fallen in the period 13 times in 20 innings against full member nations. He missed a flick off a ball from Paul van Meekeren that swung in and struck on the front pad. Rahul doesn't take a review and walks off for 9 off 12 balls.
